== 开发 ==
OmniROM 的成立是为了响应 ROM 项目CyanogenMod的商业化。<ref>{{Cite web|title=All cool kids' phones run ALTERNATIVE alternative custom Android ROM|url=https://www.theregister.com/2013/10/16/android_custom_roms_splinter_over_openness/|access-date=2021-08-08|last=Ray|first=Bill|work=www.theregister.com|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220510192042/https://www.theregister.com/2013/10/16/android_custom_roms_splinter_over_openness/}}</ref>在启动时，该项目提供了基于 [[Android_Jelly_Bean|Android Jelly Bean]]的自定义固件，并在发布后不久就转移到了[[Android_KitKat|Android KitKat]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Android 4.4 KitKat plans for AOKP, CyanogenMod, OmniROM and Paranoid Android detailed|url=https://www.androidauthority.com/android-4-4-kitkat-aokp-cyanogenmod-omnirom-paranoid-android-detailed-315786/|access-date=2021-08-08|date=2013-11-11|work=Android Authority|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210808022714/https://www.androidauthority.com/android-4-4-kitkat-aokp-cyanogenmod-omnirom-paranoid-android-detailed-315786/}}</ref>

[[Russell_Holly|Russell Holly]]表示，“OmniRom是Android的终极微调器ROM。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=OmniRom Beta for Android makes for an awesome weekend project - Geek.com|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222142211/https://www.geek.com/android/omnirom-beta-for-android-makes-for-an-awesome-weekend-project-1578564/|access-date=2021-08-08|date=2019-12-22|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>后来的一篇评论说，OmniRom是“目前为数不多的专注于社区的Android版本之一，它专注于支持尽可能多的设备，同时尽可能多地添加新功能。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Advanced Android: A look at OmniROM - Geek.com|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222142214/https://www.geek.com/android/advanced-android-a-look-at-omnirom-1596940/|access-date=2021-08-08|date=2019-12-22|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

